         <div xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574" type="decretales-l4t12">
            <head xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-Hd1e98">Titulus 12</head>
            <p xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-d1e100">
               <lb ed="#F" n="106"/>TITVLVS XII. 
      <lb ed="#F" n="107"/>DE COGNATION 
      <lb ed="#F" n="108"/>LEGALI. 
      </p>
            <div xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-Dd1e109" type="decretales-l4t12c1">
               <head xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-Hd1e111">Caput 1</head>
               <p xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-d1e113">
                  <lb ed="#F" n="109"/>CAPVT I.
      </p>
               <p xml:id="inleiv-d1e1574-d1e118">
                  <lb ed="#F" n="110"/>SI QVA. (Per adoptionem) 
      Le<lb ed="#F" n="111" break="no"/>Dgalis cognatio superioris ad 
      infe<lb ed="#F" n="112" break="no"/>riorem hoc semper prohibet, quia etiam 
      <lb ed="#F" n="113"/>collateralis impedit, dummodo durat, 
      <lb ed="#F" n="114"/>vt hic, &amp;, ff, de ritu nuptiarum per ado¬ 
      <pb ed="#F" n="474-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#F" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#F" n="1"/>ptionem. Item si filius adoptiuus cumom 
      <lb ed="#F" n="2"/>vxore adoptantis, &amp; adoptans cum vxore 
      <lb ed="#F" n="3"/>filii adoptati, etiam finita adoptione 
      contra<lb ed="#F" n="4" break="no"/>here non potest. ff. derit. nup. adoptiuus. 
      <lb ed="#F" n="5"/>Et haec vera sunt in filio arrogato, qui 
      <lb ed="#F" n="6"/>in potestatem adoptantis transit, non 
      au<lb ed="#F" n="7" break="no"/>tem in adoptato, qui non transit in 
      potesta<lb ed="#F" n="8" break="no"/>tem adoptantis. hicenim licite contrahit 
      <lb ed="#F" n="9"/>cum filijs adoptantis. Item arrogatus licitem 
      <lb ed="#F" n="10"/>contrahit cum filijs illegitimis 
      arrogan<lb ed="#F" n="11" break="no"/>tis, cum non sint in eius potestate. Alii 
      di<lb ed="#F" n="12" break="no"/>cunt idem in arrogato &amp; adoptato. arg. 
      <lb ed="#F" n="13"/>C. de adop. l. penul. §. pe. 
      </p>
